/*

Purpose:			If you select something on the table for Invoice Type Debtor Separation then we change the visibility of the buttons on the sheet

Parameters:			table	Table	The control it was performed on
					button	Integer	The button that was released to cause the event
					shift	Integer	The state of the Shift, Ctrl, and Alt keys when the mouse button was released
					x		Real	The current left physical position of the mouse pointer in the window
					y		Real	he current top physical position of the mouse pointer in the window

Return Value:		NONE

Date		Who		Reason
25 August 2022	navpw1	Initial creation TFS: 54565 (54384) - EUP - Inv Config - Invoice Surcharges

*/

begin
	self.setVisibility();
	
end;</source>
